sys_ui_message.message:
The objects and properties available to the output patterns is described below with sample data. For example:
<li><b>&#0036;&#0123event.date.fullText&#0125;</b> is replaced with <b>October 18, 32 BC</b></li>
<li><b>&#0036;&#0123person.name&#0125;</b> is replaced with <b>Chuck Tomasi</b></li>
<pre>
{
	'event' : {
		'text' : 'Something happened on this date.',
		'date' : {
			'text' : '32 BC',
			'value' : -32,
			'diff' : 2048,
			'fullText' : 'October 18, 32 BC'
		}
	},
	'now' : {
		'month' : 10,
		'day' : 18,
		'year' : {
			'value' : 2016,
			'text' : '2016'
		},
		'fullText' : 'October 18, 2016'
	},
	// birthdays and deaths only
	'person' : {
		'name' : 'Chuck Tomasi',
		'title' : 'Platform Architect',
		'born' : 1965,  // Same as event.date.text (for birthdays)
		'died' : '', // same as event.date.text (for deaths)
		'age' : 51 // same as event.date.diff (for birthdays if died != '')
	}
}</pre>
